messages.content: What are the cases handled by Ramaswamy K?

Based on the provided documents, the following cases were handled by Justice Ramaswamy K:

1. Smt. Prem Lata & Anr. Vs. M/S. Ishar Dass Chaman Lal & Ors. (Date of Judgment: 10/01/1995) - This case was an appeal by special leave from the judgment and order dated 10/01/1995 of the High Court of Delhi.
2. Shri Topandas Kundanmal, Since Deceased Thereafter By His Heir Vs. The State Through The Land Acquisition Officer, Jamnagar Etc. (Date of Judgment: 25/07/1995) - This case was a civil appeal arising from the judgment and order dated 25/07/1995 of the High Court of Gujarat.

Please note that these are the only two cases mentioned in the provided documents that were handled by Justice Ramaswamy K.
